    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/1927">Radelchis</persName> filius
                        domni bone recordationis <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, ob salute anime nostre, concessimus in <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> quod constructum esse
                        videtur infra hanc nostram Beneventanam civitatem hec est omnibus illi <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >rebus substantiis</rs> predicti cenobii ex finibus <placeName
                            key="#Geographic_regions #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/605"
                            >Ligurie</placeName> cum <rs key="#Slave">servis et ancillis</rs>
                        omnibusque suis pertinentiis quibus ęt <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> Sancti Benedicti</orgName>
                        tulerunt de potestate ipsius Sancte Sophie monasterio et dederunt illos ad
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2350">Neapolitanos</placeName>,
                        nec non et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >integris rebus</rs> illis iam dicti monasterii Sancte Sophię ex finibus
                            <placeName key="#Cities #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/112"
                            >Alifanis</placeName> et ex finibus <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/3460">Castello
                            Sancti Iohannis</placeName> seu per singulis aliis locis quibus <rs
                            key="#Slave">servis</rs> eiusdem cenobii ad <rs key="#Freeborn"
                            >liberis</rs> hominibus vel ad aliorum <rs key="#Slave">servis</rs>
                        dederunt aut per venditionem aut pigneris partibus aut aliter quomodocumque
                        ita ut a nostra potestas non siat eorum confirmata aut per capitulariam aut
                        per aliqua repromissione, sed liceat rectores prephati cenobii supra dictis
                        rebus et familiis securo nomine possidere, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo
                        et deinceps prephato monasterio Sancte Sophie et rectores eius predictis
                        rebus et familiis habere et possidere valeas per hoc nostrum roboreum
                        pręceptum et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus vel a
                        quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus possideas. Quod vero <rs key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma"
                            >preceptus concessionis</rs> ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3466">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> primo anno, mensi ianuario,
                        quarta decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
